snippet.title: Slime Evolutionary Path
snippet.description:
Today we play Slime Evolutionary Path (Not Slime Evolution, as I mistakenly called it in the video)

Slime Evolutionary Path is a cute idle game created by a single person.

Download the game here for IOS:
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/slime-evolutionary-path/id1559506738
